modName: UV Map Guide for Clothes and Skin
descriptionHtml:
Color coded UV Map. Mapping out the UV area for clothes makers so they can easily identify areas of the UV.  Its in .PSD format.  Hope you like.  :)


EDIT: Added the head UV map.  For those of you wondering why its upside down, thats because thats the correct orientation of the UV map for that particular model.  Its ok to flip it right side up so you can edit the file easier, but as soon as youre done you need to turn it upside down again so it will fit the model properly.
author: mrmysery
